@startuml
skinparam sequenceDiagram

participant User
participant uFR Nano
participant Raspberry Pi
participant WebInterface
participant PiPass
participant DB

actor User
participant uFR Nano
participant Raspberry Pi
participant WebInterface
participant PiPass
participant DB

alt [Tap First Example]
    1 Tap
    2 Polling Service
    3 Ack Tap
    4 User Lookup
    5 Zero Results
    6 Set user state to new.<br>Await WebInterface interaction.
    7 Complete Registration Workflow
else [Web Create]
    8 Start Registration Workflow
    9 Save registration.<br>Await next unassigned tap.
    10 Ack Tap
    11 User Lookup
    12 Zero Results
    13 Complete Registration
    14 Save user details
    15 Ack user registration
    16 Confirm
end

note right of User
    New User Workflow
end note

@enduml